{"chapter_number":74,"bismillah_pre":true,"revelation_order":4,"revelation_place":"makkah","name_arabic":"المدثر","name_complex":"Al-Muddaththir","name_simple":"Al-Muddaththir","verses_count":56,"pages":[575,577],"meaning":{"text":"The Cloaked One","en":"The Cloaked One","id":"Orang yang Berkemul"},"verses":[[[1,5496,"74:1","يَا أَيُّهَا الْمُدَّثِّرُ",["O you who are clothed!","Wahai orang yang berkemul (berselimut)!"],575,29,58,230,null,null],[2,5497,"74:2","قُمْ فَأَنذِرْ",["Arise and warn,","bangunlah, lalu berilah peringatan!"],575,29,58,230,null,null],[3,5498,"74:3","وَرَبَّكَ فَكَبِّرْ",["And your Lord do magnify,","dan agungkanlah Tuhanmu,"],575,29,58,230,null,null],[4,5499,"74:4","وَثِيَابَكَ فَطَهِّرْ",["And your garments do purify,","dan bersihkanlah pakaianmu,"],575,29,58,230,null,null],[5,5500,"74:5","وَالرُّجْزَ فَاهْجُرْ",["And uncleanness do shun,","dan tinggalkanlah segala (perbuatan) yang keji,"],575,29,58,230,null,null],[6,5501,"74:6","وَلَا تَمْنُن تَسْتَكْثِرُ",["And bestow not favors that you may receive again with increase,","dan janganlah engkau (Muhammad) memberi (dengan maksud) memperoleh (balasan) yang lebih banyak."],575,29,58,230,null,null],[7,5502,"74:7","وَلِرَبِّكَ فَاصْبِرْ",["And for the sake of your Lord, be patient.","Dan karena Tuhanmu, bersabarlah."],575,29,58,230,null,null],[8,5503,"74:8","فَإِذَا نُقِرَ فِي النَّاقُورِ",["For when the trumpet is sounded,","Maka apabila sangkakala ditiup,"],575,29,58,230,null,null],[9,5504,"74:9","فَذَٰلِكَ يَوْمَئِذٍ يَوْمٌ عَسِيرٌ",["That, at that time, shall be a difficult day,","maka itulah hari yang serba sulit,"],575,29,58,230,null,null],[10,5505,"74:10","عَلَى الْكَافِرِينَ غَيْرُ يَسِيرٍ",["For the unbelievers, anything but easy.","bagi orang-orang kafir tidak mudah."],575,29,58,230,null,null],[11,5506,"74:11","ذَرْنِي وَمَنْ خَلَقْتُ وَحِيدًا",["Leave Me and him whom I created alone,","Biarkanlah Aku (yang bertindak) terhadap orang yang Aku sendiri telah menciptakannya,"],575,29,58,230,null,null],[12,5507,"74:12","وَجَعَلْتُ لَهُ مَالًا مَّمْدُودًا",["And give him vast riches,","dan Aku beri kekayaan yang melimpah,"],575,29,58,230,null,null],[13,5508,"74:13","وَبَنِينَ شُهُودًا",["And sons dwelling in his presence,","dan anak-anak yang selalu bersamanya,"],575,29,58,230,null,null],[14,5509,"74:14","وَمَهَّدتُّ لَهُ تَمْهِيدًا",["And I adjusted affairs for him adjustably;","dan Aku beri kelapangan (hidup) seluas-luasnya."],575,29,58,230,null,null],[15,5510,"74:15","ثُمَّ يَطْمَعُ أَنْ أَزِيدَ",["And yet he desires that I should add more!","Kemudian dia ingin sekali agar Aku menambahnya."],575,29,58,230,null,null],[16,5511,"74:16","كَلَّا ۖ إِنَّهُ كَانَ لِآيَاتِنَا عَنِيدًا",["By no means! surely he offers opposition to Our communications.","Tidak bisa! Sesungguhnya dia telah menentang ayat-ayat Kami (Al-Qur'an)."],575,29,58,230,null,null],[17,5512,"74:17","سَأُرْهِقُهُ صَعُودًا",["I will make a distressing punishment overtake him.","Aku akan membebaninya dengan pendakian yang memayahkan."],575,29,58,230,null,null],[18,5513,"74:18","إِنَّهُ فَكَّرَ وَقَدَّرَ",["Surely he reflected and guessed,","Sesungguhnya dia telah memikirkan dan menetapkan (apa yang ditetapkannya),"],576,29,58,230,null,null],[19,5514,"74:19","فَقُتِلَ كَيْفَ قَدَّرَ",["But may he be cursed how he plotted;","maka celakalah dia! Bagaimana dia menetapkan?"],576,29,58,230,null,null],[20,5515,"74:20","ثُمَّ قُتِلَ كَيْفَ قَدَّرَ",["Again, may he be cursed how he plotted;","Sekali lagi, celakalah dia! Bagaimana dia menetapkan?"],576,29,58,230,null,null],[21,5516,"74:21","ثُمَّ نَظَرَ",["Then he looked,","Kemudian dia (merenung) memikirkan,"],576,29,58,230,null,null],[22,5517,"74:22","ثُمَّ عَبَسَ وَبَسَرَ",["Then he frowned and scowled,","lalu berwajah masam dan cemberut,"],576,29,58,230,null,null],[23,5518,"74:23","ثُمَّ أَدْبَرَ وَاسْتَكْبَرَ",["Then he turned back and was big with pride,","kemudian berpaling (dari kebenaran) dan menyombongkan diri,"],576,29,58,230,null,null],[24,5519,"74:24","فَقَالَ إِنْ هَٰذَا إِلَّا سِحْرٌ يُؤْثَرُ",["~Then he said: This is naught but enchantment, narrated (from others);","lalu dia berkata, “(Al-Qur'an) ini hanyalah sihir yang dipelajari (dari orang-orang dahulu)."],576,29,58,230,null,null],[25,5520,"74:25","إِنْ هَٰذَا إِلَّا قَوْلُ الْبَشَرِ",["This is naught but the word of a mortal.","Ini hanyalah perkataan manusia.”"],576,29,58,230,null,null],[26,5521,"74:26","سَأُصْلِيهِ سَقَرَ",["I will cast him into hell.","Kelak, Aku akan memasukkannya ke dalam (neraka) Saqar,"],576,29,58,230,null,null],[27,5522,"74:27","وَمَا أَدْرَاكَ مَا سَقَرُ",["And what will make you realize what hell is?","dan tahukah kamu apa (neraka) Saqar itu?"],576,29,58,230,null,null],[28,5523,"74:28","لَا تُبْقِي وَلَا تَذَرُ",["It leaves naught nor does it spare aught.","Ia (Saqar itu) tidak meninggalkan dan tidak membiarkan,"],576,29,58,230,null,null],[29,5524,"74:29","لَوَّاحَةٌ لِّلْبَشَرِ",["It scorches the mortal.","yang menghanguskan kulit manusia."],576,29,58,230,null,null],[30,5525,"74:30","عَلَيْهَا تِسْعَةَ عَشَرَ",["Over it are nineteen.","Di atasnya ada sembilan belas (malaikat penjaga)."],576,29,58,230,null,null],[31,5526,"74:31","وَمَا جَعَلْنَا أَصْحَابَ النَّارِ إِلَّا مَلَائِكَةً ۙ وَمَا جَعَلْنَا عِدَّتَهُمْ إِلَّا فِتْنَةً لِّلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا لِيَسْتَيْقِنَ الَّذِينَ أُوتُوا الْكِتَابَ وَيَزْدَادَ الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا إِيمَانًا ۙ وَلَا يَرْتَابَ الَّذِينَ أُوتُوا الْكِتَابَ وَالْمُؤْمِنُونَ ۙ وَلِيَقُولَ الَّذِينَ فِي قُلُوبِهِم مَّرَضٌ وَالْكَافِرُونَ مَاذَا أَرَادَ اللَّهُ بِهَٰذَا مَثَلًا ۚ كَذَٰلِكَ يُضِلُّ اللَّهُ مَن يَشَاءُ وَيَهْدِي مَن يَشَاءُ ۚ وَمَا يَعْلَمُ جُنُودَ رَبِّكَ إِلَّا هُوَ ۚ وَمَا هِيَ إِلَّا ذِكْرَىٰ لِلْبَشَرِ",["And We have not made the wardens of the fire others than angels, and We have not made their number but as a trial for those who disbelieve, that those who have been given the book may be certain and those who believe may increase in faith, and those who have been given the book and the believers may not doubt, and that those in whose hearts is a disease and the unbelievers may say: What does Allah mean by this parable? Thus does Allah make err whom He pleases, and He guides whom He pleases, and none knows the hosts of your Lord but He Himself; and this is naught but a reminder to the mortals.","Dan yang Kami jadikan penjaga neraka itu hanya dari malaikat; dan Kami menentukan bilangan mereka itu hanya sebagai cobaan bagi orang-orang kafir, agar orang-orang yang diberi kitab menjadi yakin, agar orang yang beriman bertambah imannya, agar orang-orang yang diberi kitab dan orang-orang mukmin itu tidak ragu-ragu; dan agar orang-orang yang di dalam hatinya ada penyakit dan orang-orang kafir (berkata), “Apakah yang dikehendaki Allah dengan (bilangan) ini sebagai suatu perumpamaan?” Demikianlah Allah membiarkan sesat orang-orang yang Dia kehendaki dan memberi petunjuk kepada orang-orang yang Dia kehendaki. Dan tidak ada yang mengetahui bala tentara Tuhanmu kecuali Dia sendiri. Dan Saqar itu tidak lain hanyalah peringatan bagi manusia."],576,29,58,230,null,null],[32,5527,"74:32","كَلَّا وَالْقَمَرِ",["Nay; I swear by the moon,","Tidak! Demi bulan,"],576,29,58,230,null,null],[33,5528,"74:33","وَاللَّيْلِ إِذْ أَدْبَرَ",["And the night when it departs,","dan demi malam ketika telah berlalu,"],576,29,58,230,null,null],[34,5529,"74:34","وَالصُّبْحِ إِذَا أَسْفَرَ",["And the daybreak when it shines;","dan demi subuh apabila mulai terang,"],576,29,58,230,null,null],[35,5530,"74:35","إِنَّهَا لَإِحْدَى الْكُبَرِ",["Surely it (hell) is one of the gravest (misfortunes),","sesunggunya (Saqar itu) adalah salah satu (bencana) yang sangat besar,"],576,29,58,230,null,null],[36,5531,"74:36","نَذِيرًا لِّلْبَشَرِ",["A warning to mortals,","sebagai peringatan bagi manusia,"],576,29,58,230,null,null],[37,5532,"74:37","لِمَن شَاءَ مِنكُمْ أَن يَتَقَدَّمَ أَوْ يَتَأَخَّرَ",["To him among you who wishes to go forward or remain behind.","(yaitu) bagi siapa di antara kamu yang ingin maju atau mundur."],576,29,58,230,null,null],[38,5533,"74:38","كُلُّ نَفْسٍ بِمَا كَسَبَتْ رَهِينَةٌ",["Every soul is held in pledge for what it earns,","Setiap orang bertanggung jawab atas apa yang telah dilakukannya,"],576,29,58,230,null,null],[39,5534,"74:39","إِلَّا أَصْحَابَ الْيَمِينِ",["Except the people of the right hand,","kecuali golongan kanan,"],576,29,58,230,null,null],[40,5535,"74:40","فِي جَنَّاتٍ يَتَسَاءَلُونَ",["In gardens, they shall ask each other","berada di dalam surga, mereka saling menanyakan,"],576,29,58,230,null,null],[41,5536,"74:41","عَنِ الْمُجْرِمِينَ",["About the guilty:","tentang (keadaan) orang-orang yang berdosa,"],576,29,58,230,null,null],[42,5537,"74:42","مَا سَلَكَكُمْ فِي سَقَرَ",["What has brought you into hell?","”Apa yang menyebabkan kamu masuk ke dalam (neraka) Saqar?”"],576,29,58,230,null,null],[43,5538,"74:43","قَالُوا لَمْ نَكُ مِنَ الْمُصَلِّينَ",["They shall say: We were not of those who prayed;","Mereka menjawab, “Dahulu kami tidak termasuk orang-orang yang me-laksanakan shalat,"],576,29,58,230,null,null],[44,5539,"74:44","وَلَمْ نَكُ نُطْعِمُ الْمِسْكِينَ",["And we used not to feed the poor;","dan kami (juga) tidak memberi makan orang miskin,"],576,29,58,230,null,null],[45,5540,"74:45","وَكُنَّا نَخُوضُ مَعَ الْخَائِضِينَ",["And we used to enter into vain discourse with those who entered into vain discourses.","bahkan kami biasa berbincang (untuk tujuan yang batil), bersama orang-orang yang membicarakannya,"],576,29,58,230,null,null],[46,5541,"74:46","وَكُنَّا نُكَذِّبُ بِيَوْمِ الدِّينِ",["And we used to call the day of judgment a lie;","dan kami mendustakan hari pembalasan,"],576,29,58,230,null,null],[47,5542,"74:47","حَتَّىٰ أَتَانَا الْيَقِينُ",["Till death overtook us.","sampai datang kepada kami kematian.”"],576,29,58,230,null,null],[48,5543,"74:48","فَمَا تَنفَعُهُمْ شَفَاعَةُ الشَّافِعِينَ",["So the intercession of intercessors shall not avail them.","Maka tidak berguna lagi bagi mereka syafaat (pertolongan) dari orang-orang yang memberikan syafaat."],577,29,58,230,null,null],[49,5544,"74:49","فَمَا لَهُمْ عَنِ التَّذْكِرَةِ مُعْرِضِينَ",["What is then the matter with them, that they turn away from the admonition","Lalu mengapa mereka (orang-orang kafir) berpaling dari peringatan (Allah)?"],577,29,58,230,null,null],[50,5545,"74:50","كَأَنَّهُمْ حُمُرٌ مُّسْتَنفِرَةٌ",["As if they were asses taking fright","seakan-akan mereka keledai liar yang lari terkejut,"],577,29,58,230,null,null],[51,5546,"74:51","فَرَّتْ مِن قَسْوَرَةٍ",["That had fled from a lion?","lari dari singa."],577,29,58,230,null,null],[52,5547,"74:52","بَلْ يُرِيدُ كُلُّ امْرِئٍ مِّنْهُمْ أَن يُؤْتَىٰ صُحُفًا مُّنَشَّرَةً",["Nay; every one of them desires that he may be given pages spread out;","Bahkan setiap orang dari mereka ingin agar diberikan kepadanya lembaran-lembaran (kitab) yang terbuka."],577,29,58,230,null,null],[53,5548,"74:53","كَلَّا ۖ بَل لَّا يَخَافُونَ الْآخِرَةَ",["Nay! but they do not fear the hereafter.","Tidak! Sebenarnya mereka tidak takut kepada akhirat."],577,29,58,230,null,null],[54,5549,"74:54","كَلَّا إِنَّهُ تَذْكِرَةٌ",["Nay! it is surely an admonition.","Tidak! Sesungguhnya (Al-Qur'an) itu benar-benar suatu peringatan."],577,29,58,230,null,null],[55,5550,"74:55","فَمَن شَاءَ ذَكَرَهُ",["So whoever pleases may mind it.","Maka barangsiapa menghendaki, tentu dia mengambil pelajaran darinya."],577,29,58,230,null,null],[56,5551,"74:56","وَمَا يَذْكُرُونَ إِلَّا أَن يَشَاءَ اللَّهُ ۚ هُوَ أَهْلُ التَّقْوَىٰ وَأَهْلُ الْمَغْفِرَةِ",["And they will not mind unless Allah please. He is worthy to be feared and worthy to forgive.","Dan mereka tidak akan mengambil pelajaran darinya (Al-Qur'an) kecuali (jika) Allah menghendakinya. Dialah Tuhan yang patut (kita) bertakwa kepada-Nya dan yang berhak memberi ampunan."],577,29,58,230,null,null]],[[[1,10,575,"&#xfbac;","word","يَا أَيُّهَا",["O you",""]],[2,10,575,"&#xfbad;","word","الْمُدَّثِّرُ",["who covers himself",""]],[3,10,575,"&#